title: This Woman Only Dates Married Men?!
description:
A listener reached out concerned about the possibility of being exposed by her friend for being a homewrecker. Because of this she reached out to prematurely defend herself.
Yes, she has a type when it comes to dating. She only dates married men! But before you start to judge, listen to her reasoning.
